    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of numerous devices used for taking hold of objects, consisting commonly of two pieces that are joined at one end or near one end by a pivot or spring, forming the two jaws which are used for gripping.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
